==Useful Info==
'''Pale draconians''' are the [[steam]]-themed members of the [[list of draconians|draconian]] family, with weaker breath attacks. They only appear in a select few [[vault]]s.

{{monster spells}}

==Tips & Tricks==
*[[Fire resistance]] grants steam resistance, which makes you immune to steam clouds.
*Their steam breath attacks block all lines of sight, creating a perfect opportunity for you to flee from combat without drawing an entire draconian pack with you.

==History==
*Prior to [[0.17]], pale draconians could appear in [[Zot]].
